At ITT, we are curious and agile, and continuously learn from each other by valuing different ideas, opinions and experiences.








Careers at ITT



A great company is measured by its people. We have approximately 9,400 employees worldwide, and every day they harness their bold thinking, collective know-how and impeccable character to create an enduring impact in the world.
At ITT, we focus not just on "the numbers" but also on inspiring our people. We strive to make our work environment inclusive and welcoming. By encouraging a healthy, high-performing culture and by making our customers central to everything we do, we create an atmosphere that enhances innovation and the success of our talented employees.
This innovation is crucial as we seek to solve complex challenges in key sectors of the world economy and serve our global customers. If you are inspired to help make the world a better place through new ideas, consider joining us. Explore the diverse career opportunities available at ITT today. Search for open positions now.





