ITT Products




Animate your scene with sound! ITT Products makes it easy…
Good selection of sounds modules from Innovative Train Technologies for your model railroading layout or diorama. Electrical hook up can be done to a variety of power sources.  Pre recorded original sound clips are up to 60 seconds in length. Activate sound in a number of ways or run in a continuous loop.
To listen to a particular sound module, click on the corresponding image of the product.
Click on thumbnail image for product close-up. Move cursor to upper right corner of frame and click NEXT for additonnal images. Move cursor to bottom right corner of frame and click CLOSE to return to product.
SUGARCUBE SPEAKER GLX-SCS-01Prewired and enclosed small speaker with great sound output. Black painted resin cast box. 6" wire leads. Great for DCC installations with very little space or sound modules. Small 53/64" x 39/64" x 13/32" design. 21 x 15.3 x 10 mm. 600mW power capacity. Advanced triple magnet concept provides optimized acoustic sensitivity. 8 ohms.$10.00




